						               													<description>The Roman temple of &amp;Eacute;vora was probably built in honor of Emperor Augustus. It was built in the 1st century AD in the main square (forum) of &amp;Eacute;vora - then called Liberalitas Julia.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this game players will play the role of builders of the Roman Empire and the action takes place in &amp;Eacute;vora in the 1st century AD.&amp;#10;The objective: Build the 14 columns that still exist today on the site.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players move their workers around the rondel to define the action they intend to perform: Build (stones and capitals), improve the columns already built (points multiplier) and request the influence of important characters (cards).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;These characters are:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    The Emperor who will value the columns at the end of the game.&amp;#10;    The governor who will inspect the columns and during the game will compensate the player.&amp;#10;    The centurion who maintain order in the construction site and will offer greater mobility to the player.&amp;#10;    The architect who helps in the construction process making it much more effective and profitable.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player who obtains the most prestige points, based on the stones placed in each column and also on bonuses, wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;O templo romano de &amp;Eacute;vora foi provavelmente constru&amp;iacute;do em homenagem ao imperador Augusto, que era venerado como um deus, durante e ap&amp;oacute;s seu reinado.&amp;#10;Foi constru&amp;iacute;do no s&amp;eacute;culo I d.C. na pra&amp;ccedil;a principal (f&amp;oacute;rum) de &amp;Eacute;vora - ent&amp;atilde;o chamada de Liberalitas Julia.Neste jogo os jogadores desempenhar&amp;atilde;o o papel de construtores do Imp&amp;eacute;rio Romano e a a&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o ocorre em &amp;Eacute;vora no s&amp;eacute;culo I d.C.&amp;#10;O objectivo: Construir as 14 colunas que ainda existem nos dias de hoje no local.&amp;#10;Este jogo tem a sua mec&amp;acirc;nica principal baseada num rondel e os jogadores movimentam os seus trabalhadores para definirem a a&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que pretendem executar: Construir (pedras e capiteis), aperfei&amp;ccedil;oar as colunas j&amp;aacute; constru&amp;iacute;das (multiplicador de pontos) e solicitar a influ&amp;ecirc;ncia de personagens importantes (cartas).&amp;#10;Estas personagens s&amp;atilde;o:&amp;#10;O Imperador que valorizar&amp;aacute; as constru&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es no final do jogo.&amp;#10;O governador que inspecionar&amp;aacute; as constru&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e durante o jogo compensar&amp;aacute; o jogador.&amp;#10;O centuri&amp;atilde;o que mant&amp;ecirc;m a ordem no estaleiro e oferecer&amp;aacute; maior mobilidade ao jogador.&amp;#10;O arquiteto que ajuda no processo de constru&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o tornando-o muito mais eficaz e rent&amp;aacute;vel.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Vence o jogador que obtiver mais pontos de prestigio  baseado nas pedras colocadas em cada coluna e tamb&amp;eacute;m nalgumas bonifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
